#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:167
#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_mask_and_paste_base.cpp:172
msgid ""
"Global clearance ratio between pads and the solder paste as a percentage of "
